---
import Section from "../ui/Section.astro";
---

<Section id="faq" title="FAQs">
  <div class="grid grid--2">
    <div class="card">
      <details open>
        <summary>When will I see results?</summary>
        <p class="muted">Consistency matters. Results vary based on habits and frequency (placeholder).</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Is it safe?</summary>
        <p class="muted">Gentle approach. Stop if you feel pain. This is not medical advice (placeholder).</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Do I need equipment?</summary>
        <p class="muted">No. Just your hands + consistency.</p>
      </details>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <details open>
        <summary>How do I access the course?</summary>
        <p class="muted">You purchase on the platform; access is granted there. This site links to it.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>How long is the routine?</summary>
        <p class="muted">Placeholder: about 10–15 minutes per day.</p>
      </details>

      <details>
        <summary>Can I unsubscribe from emails?</summary>
        <p class="muted">Yes. Every email includes an unsubscribe link.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    details{ padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-2); }
    details:last-child{ border-bottom: none; }
    summary{
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: var(--font-serif);
      font-size: 18px;
      list-style: none;
      outline: none;
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
    summary::after{
      content:"+";
      float:right;
      color: rgba(17,17,17,0.55);
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    details[open] summary::after{ content:"–"; }
    p{ margin: 10px 0 0; }
  </style>
</Section>
